==============================================
README for the SystemC CCI 1.0.1 documentation
==============================================

This directory contains

doxygen/ 

  A folder containing a command file (template) for doxygen which may be
  used to generate browseable documentation of the CCI class library.
  Please see www.doxygen.org for usage.

archived/

  Documentation from earlier versions of SystemC CCI, much of which is now
  out-of-date.  Please consult the Configuration, Control & Inspection 
  Language Reference Manual version 1.0 for the standard definition. This document 
  can be found on accellera.org:
  https://www.accellera.org/images/downloads/standards/systemc/SystemC_CCI_1_0_LRM.pdf

SystemC_Configuration_Tutorial.pdf

  A presentation outlining the capabilities of the SystemC Configuration standard.

README - this file.
